 and blessings be upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27659,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/16\/sawm-shaban-ramadan-together\/","url_meta":{"origin":27531,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: The Prophet fasts Sha\u2019ban and Ramadan together","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: I did not see the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, fast for two consecutive months in a row except for Sha\u2019ban and Ramadan. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 736 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0635\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38897,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/23\/connect-ramadan-shaban\/","url_meta":{"origin":27531,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sha\u2019ban: The Prophet connects fasting Ramadan and Sha\u2019ban","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 23, 20